# Percona Grafana Fork — Cursor Entry Point

Read AGENTS.md for the complete development guide covering Percona's delta over upstream Grafana, PMM UI architecture, backend routes, state management, API patterns, and testing.

## PMM Context

This is a fork of Grafana https://github.com/grafana/grafana for PMM (Percona Monitoring and Management) https://github.com/percona/pmm.
See https://github.com/percona/pmm/blob/v3/AGENTS.md for the product-wide overview.

